This #EqualPayDay & every day @HouseDemocrats stand committed to helping #WomenSucceed. Let’s end the wage gap once & for all!
Due to the wage gap, on average, women employed full time in the US lose a combined total of nearly $500 billion every year. #EqualPayDay
If the annual wage gap were eliminated, on avg, a working woman would have enough $ for approximately 1.6 years’ worth of food. #EqualPayDay
Mothers are primary or sole breadwinners in nearly 40% of families, yet the wage gap for moms is larger than for women overall. #EqualPayDay
We must pass the Paycheck Fairness Act to address the wage gap that persists regardless of industry or education level. #EqualPayDay
On average, women in America are paid 79 cents for every dollar paid to men. It's 2016 & that's simply unacceptable. #EqualPayDay
